5.robo race x=2,n=3,y=1,m=4 the smallest point meet at the starting point is 5sec->y=1+n=4=5
#i/p:1 2  1 4
#o/p:5
x,n,y,m=map(int,input().split())
time=max(x,y)
while True:
    if time>=x and (time-x)%n==0 and time>=y and (time-y)%m==0:
        print(time)
        break
    time+=1'''5.robo race x=2,n=3,y=1,m=4 the smallest point meet at the starting point is 5sec->y=1+n=4=5
#i/p:1 2  1 4
#o/p:5
